5399a2ec-1cfa-4461-8f3c-4771a41d0164	6bb9f408-86b0-41c5-89fb-5329da536690	Kangaroo Jerky Natural Pet Treats | Sniff & Bites	kangaroo-jerky-natural-pet-treats-sniff-bites	\N	<p data-start="1558" data-end="1739"><strong data-start="1558" data-end="1565">🐾 Fei Fei’s Notes:</strong> “Chicken cubes? I could train my humans for these! 🍗🐶”</p>	<p data-start="3043" data-end="3096"><strong data-start="3043" data-end="3096">Kangaroo Jerky Natural Pet Treats - Sniff &amp; Bites</strong></p>\n<p data-start="3098" data-end="3256">Lean, nutritious, and full of flavour — <strong data-start="3138" data-end="3189">Sniff &amp; Bites Kangaroo Jerky Natural Pet Treats</strong> by Sniff &amp; Frolic offer a unique protein snack your pet will love.</p>\n<p data-start="3258" data-end="3468">Kangaroo meat is naturally lean and high in protein while being lower in fat than many traditional meats. It is also considered a novel protein, making it a great option for pets with common food sensitivities.</p>\n<p data-start="3470" data-end="3661">Slowly dried to maintain its natural flavour and nutrients, this jerky provides a chewy and satisfying texture that dogs enjoy. It can also be broken into smaller pieces for training rewards.</p>\n<p data-start="3663" data-end="3735">Simple ingredients, bold flavour, and a protein source pets go wild for.</p>\n<p data-start="3737" data-end="3788">📦 Pack Size: 40 g<br data-start="3755" data-end="3758" />📅 Shelf Life: Up to 12 months</p>\n<p data-start="3790" data-end="3800">⭐ <strong>Features</strong></p>\n<p data-start="3802" data-end="3982">🦘 Lean kangaroo meat, high-protein treat<br data-start="3843" data-end="3846" />🌿 Single-ingredient novel protein<br data-start="3880" data-end="3883" />💪 Naturally low in fat<br data-start="3906" data-end="3909" />🐾 Great for pets with food sensitivities<br data-start="3950" data-end="3953" />🐶 Suitable for dogs and cats</p>	simple	published	f	1200	\N	CAD	instock	0	f	https://sniffnfrolic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/