04415489-9cac-4026-9642-7e20f8e70d1d	6bb9f408-86b0-41c5-89fb-5329da536690	Freeze-Dried Chicken Natural Pet Treats | Sniff & Bites	freeze-dried-chicken-natural-pet-treats-sniff-bites	\N	<p data-start="1558" data-end="1739"><strong data-start="1558" data-end="1565">🐾 Fei Fei’s Notes:</strong> “Chicken cubes? I could train my humans for these! 🍗🐶”</p>	<h3>Freeze-Dried Chicken Natural Pet Treats - Sniff &amp; Bites</h3>\n<p>Simple, pure, and packed with protein — Sniff &amp; Bites Freeze-Dried Chicken Natural Pet Treats by <strong>Sniff &amp; Frolic</strong> are made from <strong>100% chicken</strong> and gently freeze-dried to lock in natural flavour and nutrients.</p>\n<p>Freeze-drying helps preserve the natural taste and nutritional value of fresh meat without the need for additives or preservatives. These treats are high in lean protein, making them perfect for training rewards, everyday snacks, or meal toppers.</p>\n<p>Because they contain only one ingredient, they are ideal for pets with sensitive digestion or limited-ingredient diets. Light, crunchy, and irresistible, they are loved by both dogs and cats.</p>\n<p>📦 Pack Size: 40 g<br />\n📅 Shelf Life: Up to 12 months</p>\n<p>⭐ <strong>Features</strong></p>\n<p>🍗 100% chicken single-ingredient treat<br />\n💪 High-protein snack for strong muscles<br />\n🌿 No additives, fillers, or preservatives<br />\n🐾 Freeze-dried to preserve flavour and nutrients<br />\n🐶 Suitable for dogs and cats</p>	simple	published	f	1000	\N	CAD	instock	0	f	https://sniffnfrolic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/freeze-dried-chicken-natural-pet-treats-sniff-bites-02.png	2026-03-31 21:08:38.318338+00	2026-03-31 23:47:27.022983+00	7517	2026-03-04 20:26:24+00	2026-03-05 00:01:36+00	2026-03-31 23:47:27.022983+00
0db76509-a6cd-4c4b-a176-e8a342ab752b	6451da69-cdc8-4497-8299-db64f0cc5a0a	Dusten Denim Dog Jacket – Silver Paw	dusten-denim-dog-jacket-silver-paw	SJPJ6971	<p data-start="1558" data-end="1739"><strong data-start="1558" data-end="1565">🐾 Fei Fei’s Notes:</strong> “Denim days are my fave days! Looking cool, feeling free – I’m basically a rock star on four paws! 👖✨”</p>	<h3><strong>Dusten Denim Dog Jacket – Silver Paw</strong></h3>\n<p data-start="339" data-end="599">Let your pup rock the ultimate Canadian tuxedo with the <strong data-start="444" data-end="485">Dusten Denim Dog Jacket by Silver Paw</strong>. Designed for pups who love timeless street style, this lightweight denim jacket combines fashion and function.</p>\n<p data-start="601" data-end="843">Made from a flexible cotton-poly-spandex blend, it offers comfort and easy movement. The <strong data-start="690" data-end="724">Silverpooch poop bag dispenser</strong> keeps clean-ups convenient, while a smart <strong data-start="767" data-end="794">buttonhole leash access</strong> lets you clip the collar or harness with ease.</p>\n<p data-start="845" data-end="1056">With its <strong data-start="854" data-end="881">distressed denim finish</strong> and <strong data-start="886" data-end="914">durable double-stitching</strong>, this jacket brings effortless cool to every walk. From city strolls to café hangouts, your dog will look chic and feel comfy all day long.</p>\n<p data-start="1508" data-end="1523">⭐ <strong>Features</strong></p>\n<p data-start="1525" data-end="1768">👖 Classic distressed denim look<br data-start="1567" data-end="1570" />🐾 Built-in Silverpooch poop bag dispenser<br data-start="1612" data-end="1615" />🔗 Buttonhole leash access for collar or harness<br data-start="1663" data-end="1666" />🧵 Stretch fabric for comfort and mobility<br data-start="1708" data-end="1711" />💪 Durable and machine washable<br data-start="1742" data-end="1745" />🎨 Designed in Canada</p>	variable	published	f	0	\N	CAD	outofsto