 it satisfies their natural instincts.</p>\n<p><strong>⭐ Product Features</strong><br />\n• Durable natural rubber<br />\n• Treat-dispensing rocket body<br />\n• Multiple stuffing locations<br />\n• Slow-feeding capability<br />\n• Safe and veterinarian approved<br />\n• Dishwasher-safe and easy to clean<br />\n• Suitable for indoor and outdoor use</p>\n<p><strong>⭐ Key Benefits</strong><br />\n• Reduces boredom and separation anxiety<br />\n• Encourages sniffing and problem-solving<br />\n• Supports healthy chewing habits<br />\n• Helps protect furniture from chewing<br />\n• Improves digestion when used for slow feeding<br />\n• Promotes calm behaviour after enrichment</p>\n<p><strong>🐶 Suitable For</strong><br />\n• Small to large dogs<br />\n• Moderate to heavy chewers<br />\n• Puppies developing healthy habits<br />\n• Dogs needing mental enrichment<br />\n• Indoor, crate, or travel use</p>\n<p><strong>🍖 How to Use</strong><br />\n• Stuff with peanut butter or yogurt<br />\n• Fill with kibble for slow feeding<br />\n• Freeze with wet food for extra challenge<br />\n• Use during crate training or quiet time<br />\n• Supervise during the first few uses</p>\n<p><strong>🧵 Material</strong><br />\nNatural rubber (BPA-free, food-safe, non-toxic, USA-made)</p>\n<p><strong>📏 Size / Dimensions</strong><br />\nApprox. 4″ height × 3¼″ width<br />\nSuitable for dogs 30–60 lb</p>\n<p><strong>🧼 Care Instructions</strong><br />\n• Dishwasher safe (top rack)<br />\n• Hand wash with warm soapy water<br />\n• Allow to dry fully before next use</p>\n<p><strong>SodaPup Official Website:</strong><br />\n<a href="https://sodapup.com/">https://sodapup.com/</a></p>	simple	draft	f	1680	\N	CAD	instock	0	f	https://sniffnfrolic.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sodapup-rocketman-1.webp	2026-03-31 21:08:39.620501+00	2026-03-31 23:47:28.42123+00	2073	2025-07-09 02:46:35+00	2025-12-15 05:57:15+00	2026-03-31 23:47:28.42123+00
